channel.title: Internet Protocol Problems
channel.description:
Hello, i'm having a few problems with MoparScape at the moment. When I try to connect to any server, if the internet protocol (IP Address) is redirected internet protocol (xxx.no-ip.org) for some reason I can't connect. If the internet protocol is straight through (00.00.00.00) then it allows me to connect.
Can anyone tell me how to allow the redirect protocol?
